Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.02,0:22:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}そう　この出会いが　運命でも　偶然でも　いいの
