Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.17,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}そう　迷う日々も　どんなときも
