Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.82,0:21:52.54,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}只是想要慎重的守護著
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.86,0:21:58.21,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}打從心底滲入
