Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.06,0:22:18.98,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}即使身處夢中也好    只想陪伴彼此身邊
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.04,0:22:24.75,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}神明大人一定
