Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.02,0:22:42.93,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}縱使這場邂逅    是命運也好    是偶然也罷
Dialogue: 1,0:22:42.96,0:22:48.80,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}我們兩人之間
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.06,0:22:55.15,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}不幸難以遭遇
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.17,0:23:02.56,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}也許迷惘之日    無論任何時候
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.58,0:23:09.26,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}只要積極向前    便能綻放笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.98,0:23:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,前段時間的那個  準備怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.27,0:23:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,前段時間的那個…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.14,0:23:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,對   就是那個啊   那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.81,0:23:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的   關於那個   我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.56,0:23:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那個究竟是…
